cs.FL, cs.QL, cs.IT, cs.DS, cs.LO

Reasoning: 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with finite automata and language recognition.
- cs.QL (Quantum Physics) is also likely as the paper discusses quantum finite automata.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper deals with the recognition of languages and the associated information content.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper presents new constructions for the automata.
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is also relevant as the paper deals with the recognition of languages and the associated logical properties.
